			<p>Once there was a navigation concept established, I felt comfortable moving forward with some sketches of the actual UI. One challenge was designing a single interface for two totally separate audiences: buyers and sellers. I looked to a few mobile apps like Airbnb and eBay for some inspiration around the idea of serving separate audiences on either end of a transaction.
